data.description: Welcome to beautiful Thousand Palms, centrally located in the Coachella Valley, only a few minutes from the airport, music festivals, Acrisure Arena, and so much more. This home was built with absolute quality throughout. 4 bedrooms 2 bathrooms with an open floor plan, high ceilings and very spacious throughout. Big courtyard in the front entrance, and nice long patio in the backyard, this property has all the makings of a true Desert getaway home. Beautiful neighborhood to raise your family yet quiet and serene enough to refresh, reenergize, and refocus. RV PARKING is an understatement here with plenty of room and actual electric hookup for your rigs to power up. Spacious 2 car garage with a workshop style setup. All Appliances included, tool shed included, and central air that is only 2 years old. Elevation certificate is provided so no need for flood insurance. VA ASSUMABLE LOAN also available on this file.  Schedule your appointments and let's get you moving!!
